### NewsApp API — Fichier de tests HTTP
### Compatible VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP Client
### Ordre recommande : Auth -> News -> Posts -> Favorites -> Users -> Admin

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

